<!-- Session 3: The 4-7-8 Sleep Switch -->
<!-- Duration Target: 20 minutes -->
<!-- Designed for pre-sleep relaxation -->

<!-- Opening - Very calm, slow delivery -->
<p>
<s>Welcome to your sleep preparation session.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Tonight, you will learn a technique that can become your natural sleep switch.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>A simple pattern of breathing that tells your body and mind: it's time to rest.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Make yourself comfortable now.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>If you're in bed, that's perfect.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Let your body sink into the mattress.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Feel how the bed rises to meet you, supporting every part of your body.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Close your eyes if they aren't already closed.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Let your eyelids become heavy.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Let them rest.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>There's nothing you need to see right now.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>There's nothing you need to do.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<!-- Progressive Relaxation -->
<p>
<s>Let's begin with a gentle body scan.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>I'll guide you to release tension from each area of your body.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Simply notice what I mention, and let it soften.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your forehead.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Notice any tension there. The furrows. The tightness.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>And let it smooth. Let it release.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Your eyes and the muscles around them.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Softening.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Your jaw.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Let your mouth open slightly. Tongue resting. Jaw unclenched.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your neck and shoulders.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Where so much tension lives.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Let them drop. Let them release toward the earth.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Your arms.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Heavy now. Resting wherever they are.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Your hands.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Fingers uncurling. Palms open.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your chest.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Notice how it rises and falls with each breath.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>No effort needed. Breathing happens on its own.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Your belly.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Soft. No holding. No tension.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Your lower back, hips, and pelvis.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Releasing into the bed.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your legs.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Heavy. Sinking.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Your feet.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Toes uncurling. All tension draining away.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Your whole body now.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Soft. Heavy. At rest.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<!-- Introduction to 4-7-8 -->
<p>
<s>Now I'll teach you the four-seven-eight breath.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>This technique was developed by Dr. Andrew Weil, based on ancient yogic breathing practices.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>He calls it a natural tranquilizer for the nervous system.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<p>
<s>The pattern is simple.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Inhale quietly through your nose for four counts.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Hold your breath gently for seven counts.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Exhale completely through your mouth, making a soft whoosh sound, for eight counts.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>That's one cycle.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<p>
<s>The exhale is longer than the inhale.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>This is the key.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>The extended exhale activates your parasympathetic nervous system.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>It sends a signal to your brain: we are safe. We can rest.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Before we begin, place the tip of your tongue against the ridge of tissue just behind your upper front teeth.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Keep it there throughout the practice.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>This is a subtle but important detail from the traditional technique.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<!-- Round 1 - Fully Guided -->
<p>
<s>Let's do the first breath together.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Exhale completely first, emptying your lungs.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Now, inhale quietly through your nose.</s>
