<s>There's nothing more to do.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Nothing to fix. Nothing to figure out.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Just rest.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your nervous system knows what to do from here.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>You've given it the signal.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>The extended exhales have activated your parasympathetic system.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Your heart rate is slowing.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Your muscles are releasing.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Your brain waves are shifting toward sleep.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<!-- Sleep Transition -->
<p>
<s>From here, you can simply drift.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>There's no effort required.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Sleep will find you when you're ready.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>If thoughts arise, let them pass.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Like clouds drifting through a night sky.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>You don't need to chase them.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>You don't need to solve anything.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Just let them float by.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Your only job now is to rest.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>To receive the gift of sleep.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>To surrender into the dark, soft comfort of the night.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<!-- Final Suggestions -->
<p>
<s>In a moment, my voice will fade away.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
