<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>And within that silence, peace.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Remember, you can use the four-seven-eight breath anytime you need to calm your mind.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Before falling asleep.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>If you wake in the night.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>In moments of stress or anxiety.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>It's your natural tranquilizer. Always available.</s>
